MM7DRead - Status reader program for MM7D device
------------------------------------------------

1. About software
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  You can check status of mm7d growing house controllers with this
software via network.

The package includes a GUI application and three command-line scripts.
Everything can be queried with the GUI program. With the scripts only
the measured data in different format (CSV, JSON, TXT and XML) and
protocol (HTTP, Modbus/TCP and Modbus/RTU). 

The 'wget' program required for the 'mm7dread-http' script to work can
be found in all Linux distributions, install it with the package manager.
The 'modpoll' program required for 'mm7dread-modbus-*' scripts to work
can be downloaded from <https://www.modbusdriver.com/modpoll.html>.

2. How to get installer package for my OS?
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
a. Visit homepage (see later) to download installer packages:

  architecture  operation system        filename
  ---------------------------------------------------------------
  (all)         (source code)           mm7dread-0.4.tar.gz
  i386          Linux                   mm7dread-0.4-i386.bin
  i386          Linux                   mm7dread-0.4-i386.tar.gz
  i386          Debian GNU/Linux        mm7dread_0.4-1_i386.deb
  amd64         Linux                   mm7dread-0.4-amd64.bin
  amd64         Linux                   mm7dread-0.4-amd64.tar.gz
  amd64         Debian GNU/Linux        mm7dread_0.4-1_amd64.deb

The source package can be compiled for arm, i386 and amd64 processors,
FreeBSD, Linux and Windows operating systems. The source package also
contains the necessary files for packaging.

b. Download from Github

  $ git clone https://github.com/pozsarzs/mm7dread.git

c. Download from Debian repository

  set reporitory:
  # echo "deb http://www.pozsarzs.hu/deb/ ./" >> /etc/apt/sources.list
  # wget -q -O - http://www.pozsarzs.hu/deb/KEY.gpg | apt-key add -
  # apt-get update

  install
  # apt-get install mm7dread

